ygData.subject: Re: Online marriage and RL relationships
ygData.msgSnippet: I m single in Real Life.  I used to get into Internet Relationships but I ve found that they usually end badly. =(.. I ve spent too much time mourning over
ygData.messageBody:
I'm single in Real Life. I used to get into Internet Relationships but I've
found that they usually end badly. =(.. I've spent too much time mourning over
lost Net-relationships, so unless I find someone online who I am TOTALLY
compatible with and who lives in a relatively close distance to me so a real
relationship is viable I'm shying away from the whole thing. I tell anyone
who's interested in me that any relationship will stay on the 'net and no real
life feelings other than friendship and affection will be involved. =)

-=Annwyl Anklestabber-Northoak=-
(Aka Tori)
